Date: Mon 19 Apr 2004
From: Joseph Dudley <jdudley@intellibridge.com>
Source: The Hindu 18 Apr 2004 [edited]
<http://www.hindu.com/2004/04/19/stories/2004041910110100.htm>

Anthrax Affects 2 More
--------------------------------
2 more persons today fell ill following the outbreak of anthrax in West
Bengal's Murshidabad district, taking the number of persons suffering from
the disease to 23.
--
Joseph P. Dudley, Ph.D.
